OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will stay
OL,6,Fdry through the evening and overnight.
OL,7,FEvening sunshine will lead to clear
OL,8,Fspells overnight allowing some patchy
OL,9,Fmist or frost to develop.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FDry and bright in the
OL,12,Fmorning after a chilly start. Becoming
OL,13,Fwarm again by day, with sunshine
OL,14,Fturning hazy as it becomes cloudier at
OL,15,Ftimes later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
