OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHigh
OL,6,Fpressure will maintain mainly dry and
OL,7,Fsettled weather with sunshine at
OL,8,Ftimes, but chance of the odd shower on
OL,9,FSunday and Monday. Quite warm inland
OL,10,Fbut cooler along coasts.
